message.content:
cs.NI, cs.CR, cs.DC, cs.SY, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on networking smartphones for disaster recovery.
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is also likely as the paper may discuss security concerns related to the messaging and self-rescue systems.
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is a possibility as the paper may discuss the distributed nature of the messaging and self-rescue systems.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possibility as the paper may discuss the design and implementation of the TeamPhone system.
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possibility as the paper may discuss the use of multimedia (e.g. location and position information) in the self-rescue system.
